item.title: Socket Class v1.3.0.9
item.description:
Product: Socket Class v1.3.0.9
Company: NIST
Release Date: Thu, 16 Nov 2017 10:09:36 -0500
Packager: Allen Goldstein

Description: Socket class: A low-level networking API. Currently there are two child classes, Socket.TCP and Socket.UDP.

Release Notes: Packet size type increased from uint16 to uint32.
Python example code now receives very large data.
item.dc:creator: NIST
